            <title>[LU-5189] add debian kernel detection support to lustre</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5189</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i&apos;am building a cluster with lustre on Debian Squeeze on amd64, and the configure doesn&apos;t detect the debian kernel. This affect ldiskfs who cannot be builded because it doesn&apos;t find the right patch series.&lt;/p&gt;
